96x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Billy-Joel-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Billy-Joel-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/billy-joel">比利乔尔</a>宣布他将在格莱美颁奖典礼上表演，这是他 22 年来首次在颁奖典礼上表演。</p><p>这位“钢琴人”歌手将与<a href="/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> 、 <a href="/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> 、 <a href="/artists/olivia-rodrigo">Olivia Rodrigo</a> 、 <a href="/artists/travis-scott">Travis Scott</a> 、 <a href="/artists/burna-boy">Burna Boy</a>和<a href="/artists/luke-combs">Luke Combs 等</a>人一起成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-scott-burna-boy-and-luke-combs-to-perform-at-2024-grammys-3574748">2024 年格莱美表演者</a>。今年的颁奖典礼将于 2 月 4 日（星期日）在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶的 Crypto.com Arena 举行。这将标志着乔尔自 2002 年与已故的托尼·贝内特 ( <a href="/artists/tony-bennett">Tony Bennett)</a>一起表演以来重返颁奖典礼舞台。</p><p>乔尔的表演将在《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-joel-announces-first-single-in-decades-with-turn-the-lights-back-on-3575040">Turn The Lights Back On</a> 》发行三天后进行，这是他自 2007 年以来的第一首个人歌曲，也是自 1993 年以来的第二首个人歌曲。该歌曲定于 2 月 1 日通过哥伦比亚发行。它将在所有流媒体平台上发售，并推出限量版 7 英寸黑胶唱片。您可以<a href="https://billyjoel.com/">在此处</a>预先保存/预订。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C2fuF-IyWkW/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow